{"tid":1898904,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實大家知唔知搵僱傭兵即係意味住要打仗?","createTime":"2020-02-26T09:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T10:54:59.000Z","uid":45100,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"277678bb28e8c7a79869c1479d56990ffba3ffc8","tid":1898904,"uid":45100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"係有彈有炮果種打仗。兵馬未動，糧草先行。點確保戰略物資供應? 一場武肺，剩係睇口罩，廁紙，米，都玩到全港死死下，仲講打仗? <br />\n順帶一提，僱傭兵係睇錢做野，我地要同對家鬥多錢&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n唔打仗請暗殺都得姐? 岩，不過點揀人殺同後果我仲未諗好。<br />\n另，歡迎認真討論物資供應鏈。在下人微言輕，時間苦短，只能首任為想辦法照顧好自身，先嘗試在家種植，正在能待工具到貨。"},{"pid":"ec2ba73ce078e7102b8d6cde418a09addbee1654","tid":1898904,"uid":45100,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"望住一街ff請僱傭兵，但好多都沒概念請黎做咩任務，就好似9叫香港人報仇一樣......<br />\n其實係咪得我認真左，大家都只係講黎開心下咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb67e24cb138c7e4d52ba25bda6509222e333eb8","tid":1898904,"uid":89641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"如果真係出真鎗打仗，有幾多忠誠勇毅會縮沙？"},{"pid":"4ce85f0d93134a204769347cd833d871bc8167d9","tid":1898904,"uid":45100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb67e24cb138c7e4d52ba25bda6509222e333eb8","tid":1898904,"uid":89641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"如果真係出真鎗打仗，有幾多忠誠勇毅會縮沙？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"唔知，我都想知到時班自稱白警既人如何自處。不過到時面對既主戰力會係老解"},{"pid":"936151cdd0896a95a67b5f09bf8bb54ce34689d5","tid":1898904,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ce85f0d93134a204769347cd833d871bc8167d9","tid":1898904,"uid":45100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb67e24cb138c7e4d52ba25bda6509222e333eb8","tid":1898904,"uid":89641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:59:54.000Z","msg"